leela-zero
------------------------------------------
Go engine with no human-provided knowledge, modeled after the AlphaGo Zero
paper.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libOpenCL1-2.3.5-1
  libQt5Core5-5.9.4-2
  libboost_filesystem1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_program_options1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_system1.66-1.66.0-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libOpenCL-devel-2.3.5-1
  libQt5Core-devel-5.9.4-2
  libboost-devel-1.66.0-1
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/leela-zero/leela-zero

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/leela-zero/leela-zero.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack leela-zero-0.17-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./leela-zero-0.17-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/leela-zero-0.17-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/leela-zero-0.17-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(leela-zero)
  /usr/lib/leelaz/autogtp.exe
  /usr/lib/leelaz/leelaz.exe
  /usr/lib/leelaz/validation.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/leela-zero.README
  /usr/share/doc/leela-zero/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/leela-zero/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/leela-zero/FAQ.md
  /usr/share/doc/leela-zero/README.md

